\eqn{I} represent the set of planning units
(indexed by \eqn{i} or \eqn{j}), \eqn{Z} represent
the set of management zones (indexed by \eqn{z} or \eqn{y}), and
\eqn{X_{iz}}{Xiz} represent the decision
