\sum_{i}^{I} \sum_{z}^{Z} (p \times W_{zz} B_{ii}) +
\sum_{i}^{I} \sum_{j}^{I} \sum_{z}^{Z}
\sum_{y}^{Z} (-2 \times p \times X_{iz} \times X_{jy} \times W_{zy} \times
B_{ij})}{
sum_i^I sum_z^Z (p * Wzz * Bii) + sum_i^I
sum_j^I sum_z^Z sum_y^Z (-2 * p * Xiz * Xjy * Wzy * Bij)
